<plot>Follow acclaimed filmmaker Goran Rosenberg on a daring documentary road trip through the U.S., exploring the movements, events, values and ideas that will shape America in the years to come. Mixing prestigious high profile interviews (politicians, celebrities, academics...) with dramatic encounters with regular people in real life situations (illegal immigrants, vigilantes, activists...), "America's Choice" exposes the many hard choices and challenges America is facing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?034468</url></doc>
